{"tid":460073,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]Tesla其實唔慢","createTime":"2017-11-06T10:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T19:59:10.000Z","uid":42760,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"77d0b427791c341994a48edbde79765c5dc8e87f","tid":460073,"uid":42760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dphw4km60m4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDphw4km60m4&d=LGXF8pnRWKgDDRU%2FAc5FZ7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d43e6e45\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dphw4km60m4</a><br />\n終於有Model S N&uuml;burgring片睇，好多嘢睇到：<br />\n1. 揸得快電池會倒水咁去，電量用得仲快過iPhone<br />\n2. 三分鐘後就著電池過熱保護，動力會愈揸愈少，一個圈後已經無咗三份一Power<br />\n3. 上斜就算係直路部車想加速都好困難<br />\n4. 雖然係四驅，但真係好推頭。咁推頭個車手仲下下拎得盡線位幾勁<br />\n5. 以大房車黎講都真係好貼伏，好多彈位伏位，例如6:43秒個落斜，都處理得好好<br />\n即係呢，部車就真係好快，但唔係設計用黎揸得快，所以最後都係唔快，不過都唔係人地講到咁慢"},{"pid":"0139dcb7814b8119c2c7236ec98ea56fa48d1dc0","tid":460073,"uid":88841,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"世事都被樓主看透了。"},{"pid":"f6f3477124c8199047a1e9d03d67c1e4db66ffe1","tid":460073,"uid":17718,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:27:11.000Z","msg":"邊個話佢慢？"},{"pid":"e8fe255d55db08d52306a583c21312a722c4e1dc","tid":460073,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"考古？？定係個post 係兩年前諗住開架？"},{"pid":"20999ddb09bc39417edf76fa3c6917b353873371","tid":460073,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"架車真係好貼服，估唔到咁唔跳"},{"pid":"7fb29cbfd9a5fe8fd68055b34f0fa7ef2b7f91f7","tid":460073,"uid":42629,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"咁鳩慢都叫快<br />\nD彎完全入唔撚倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8341f0f29e48b22c339ad76be7b3f249e5f16a85","tid":460073,"uid":147380,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"